truth across all sources of information is one of the biggest challenges faced by IT organizations today.</li><li>ETL stands for:<ul><li>Data <b>extraction</b> from source databases.</li><li>Transport of the data & data <b>transformation</b>.</li><li><b>Loading</b> of data into a database.</li></ul></li></ul>';$_['sv_content_smart_etl'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Allows data manipulations across multiple sources:<ul><li>Any database using ODBC on Windows.</li><li>MySQL/PostgreSQL/Oracle/AS/400/SQLServer/IBM-DB2.</li><li>MaxDB (SAP DB), SAP R/3 System (ProSAPCONN plugin).</li></ul></li><li>Graphical tool performs the typical data flow functions like <ul><li>  reading, validating, refining, transforming, writing data to</li>   <li>a variety of different data sources and destinations.</li>  </ul></li>  <li>Modern, Standards-based Architecture:  <ul><li>Allows remote monitoring of the running ETL processes through a web browser.100% Java with broad, cross platform support.</li><li>Repository-based providing easy re-use of queries and transformation components</li> <li>along with structured management of models, connections, logs,...</li></ul></li></ul>';$_['sv_content_when_etl'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>Application integration, lets say SmartBizPOS-Sync integrate between SmartBizERP & SmartBizPOS.</li> <li>Exploration of data in existing databases (tables, views, etc.),   let"s say SmartBizAlerts (send email/SMS to do internet marketing).</li> <li>Export of database(s) to text-file(s) or other databases.</li> <li>Import of data into databases, ranging from text-files to excel sheets.</li> <li>Data migration between database applications.</li> <li>Information enrichment by looking up data in various information stores (databases, text-files, excel sheets and more).</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_uc_application_integration'] = '<ul class="BossListContent"><li>SmartBizPOS-Sync is a data sharing and integration between ERP & POS where:<ul><li>ERP is the central repository of the data: products, customers, taxes, orders...</li><li>POS has the ability to operate with the master data downloaded from ERP and   to upload orders created by the sales activity of POS.</li>  </ul></li><li>How to share and integrate data between ERP & POS:<ul ><li>The ERP-REST-WebService operates on Business Objects in ERP.</li><li>Synchronize data:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ERP --> POS: products (& product attribute), business partner, price, inventory, tax...<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;POS --> ERP: orders, ...</li><li>How to run ETL transformations and jobs:<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Option 1: manually run using graphical tool. <br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color="#005c8f">&bull;</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Option 2: scheduled in batch mode to be run automatically at regular intervals.</li></ul>';$_['sv_content_uc_exploration_data'] = 'UC Exploration data';$_['sv_content_uc6'] = 'UC 6';// product//solution	//menu	$_['menu_smartbiz-suite']='SmartBiz Suite';	$_['menu_erp']='Enterprise Resource Planning - ERP';	$_['menu_pos']='Point Of Sales - POS';	$_['menu_bi']='Business Intelligence - BI';	$_['menu_hrm']='Human Resource - HRM';	$_['menu_ecommerce']='eCommerce';	$_['menu_relationship']='Customer Relationship';	$_['menu_rms']='Distribution Management &nbsp; System - DMS';	//smartbiz suite	$_['smartbiz_suite_content_Distribution']='	<ul class="BossListContent">	<li>SmartBiz Suite cho ngành Phân phối giúp doanh nghiệp giảm chi phí và tăng vòng quay tồn kho, hiệu quả sử dụng vốn và mức độ thỏa mãn của khách hàng:	<ul><li>Kiểm soát kho thời gian thực, hỗ trợ nhiều công ty, nhiều kho, nhiều khu vực và tính toán giá trị tồn kho</li><li>Dễ dàng quản lý tài chính để tối ưu dòng tiền và hoạt động của kho</li> <li>Mở rộng chuỗi phân p